sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C   as C Binary
    participant SRV as 2030.5 Server

    Note over C,SRV: EXI-encoded XML over TLS 1.2<br/>cipher: TLS_ECDHE_ECDSA_WITH_AES_128_CCM_8

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}/fsa/derp/{id}/derc<br/>Accept: application/sep+xml  |  mutual TLS

    SRV -->> C: 200 OK<br/>Content-Type: application/sep+xml<br/>[EXI body] DERControlList

    Note over C: decode EXI → DERControlList<br/>iterate controls, extract DERControlBase

    C   ->> SRV: GET /edev/{sfdi}/fsa/derp/{id}/derc/{mrid}

    SRV -->> C: 200 OK  [EXI body] DERControl {<br/>  mrid: "abc123"<br/>  interval: {start:1700000000, duration:900}<br/>  DERControlBase: {opModFixedW:{value:8000,multiplier:0},<br/>  rampTms:60, opModConnect:true}<br/>}

    Note over C: schedule event at start_time<br/>emit: EVENT_JSON:{type:start,...}
